 RвҶҗTest_CreateAPI_012(stopFlag batchFlag);вҺ•TRAP;noOf;folder;res;cfg
вҚқ Exercise CreateAPIfromCFG on all possible types of objects with a namespace with an additional level
 вҺ•TRAPвҶҗ(999 'C' '. вҚқ Deliberate error')(0 'N')
 RвҶҗT._Failed

 #.вҺ•SHADOW'TEMP'
 'TEMP'#.вҺ•NS''
 folderвҶҗвҲҶTEMP_TEST_DATA,'/MyApp3'
 resвҶҗвҺ•SE.Link.Import'#.TEMP'folder
 AssertвҲЁ/'Imported:'вҚ·res
 Assert~вҲЁ/'Error:'вҚ·res

 cfgвҶҗ##.Registry.GetJsonFromFile folder,'/apl-package.json'
 noOfвҶҗ##.Client.CreateAPIfromCFG #.TEMP cfg
 вҶ’T.PassesIf noOf=вүў#.TEMP.sub.вҺ•NLвҚі16

 вҶ’T.PassesIf'Universe'вүЎ#.TEMP.API.sub.HelloVars
 вҶ’T.PassesIf'Galaxy'вүЎ#.TEMP.API.sub.class1.Hello2
 вҶ’T.PassesIf'Niladic'вүЎ#.TEMP.API.sub.fn1
 вҶ’T.PassesIf'Monadic'вүЎ#.TEMP.API.sub.fn2 вҚ¬
 вҶ’T.PassesIf'Dyadic'вүЎвҚ¬ #.TEMP.API.sub.fn3 вҚ¬
 вҶ’T.PassesIf'Ambivalent'вүЎ#.TEMP.API.sub.fn4 вҚ¬
 :Trap 0
     #.TEMP.API.sub.fn5
     вҶ’T.PassesIf 1
 :Else
     вҶ’T.PassesIf 0
 :EndTrap
 вҶ’T.PassesIf 3.14вүЎ#.TEMP.API.sub.ns2.PI
 вҶ’T.PassesIf 6вүЎ#.TEMP.API.sub.dfn1вҚі3
 вҶ’T.PassesIf 9 7вүЎ#.TEMP.API.sub.dfn2 9 2
 вҶ’T.PassesIf 9вүЎ4 #.TEMP.API.sub.dfn3 5
 вҶ’T.PassesIf 0<#.TEMP.API.sub.вҺ•NC'interface1'
 вҶ’T.PassesIf'Galaxy'вүЎ#.TEMP.API.sub.ns1.Hello
 вҶ’T.PassesIf 4вҲ§.=вҠғвҲҳ#.TEMP.API.sub.вҺ•NCВЁ'op1' 'op2' 'op3' 'op4'
 вҶ’T.PassesIf 6вүЎ+/#.TEMP.API.sub.op1вҚі3
 вҶ’T.PassesIf 21вүЎ+/#.TEMP.API.sub.op2{вҚө}2 3вҚҙвҚі12
 вҶ’T.PassesIf ВҜ220вүЎ10-#.TEMP.API.sub.op3Г—22
 вҶ’T.PassesIf ВҜ6вүЎГ—/#.TEMP.API.sub.op4+вҚі3
 вҶ’T.PassesIf 0вҲ§.вү #.TEMP.API.sub.вҺ•NCвҶ‘'HelloVars' 'Hello'
 вҶ’T.PassesIf'World'вүЎ#.TEMP.API.sub.Hello

 RвҶҗT._OK
вҚқDone
